@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### Publish email
POST {{baseUrl}}/emails/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "receiver@example.com",
  "from": "sender@example.com",
  "subject": "Hello from Mail Burrow",
  "body": "This is a test email sent through the async email flow."
}

### Get email status
@emailId = paste-email-id-here

GET {{baseUrl}}/emails?id={{emailId}}
Accept: application/json
